916
01:04:10,685 --> 01:04:11,753
<i>Aku mendengarmu. Aku disini.</i>

917
01:04:11,786 --> 01:04:13,287
<i>Sekarang, kuingin kau
sambungkan aku</i>

918
01:04:13,320 --> 01:04:14,756
